org.modelio.gproject.gproject.remote

Class GRemoteProjectFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.modelio.gproject.gproject.remote.GRemoteProjectFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IProjectFactory
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GUrlProjectFactory

    public abstract class GRemoteProjectFactory
extends Object
implements IProjectFactory
    Remote project factory.

    This is the base class for all remote project factory implementations. Many methods are final, they are not meant to be redefined in order to keep the same file geometry for all remote project implementations..
